<inglise> (21) Whereas this Directive is without prejudice to the application of any national provisions which may prohibit the private possession of illicit devices, to the application of Community competition rules and to the application of Community rules concerning intellectual property rights; </inglise>
<eesti> 21) k&auml;esolev direktiiv ei piira mingite ebaseaduslike seadmete eraviisilist omamist keelustavate siseriiklike s&auml;tete kohaldamist, &uuml;henduse konkurentsieeskirjade kohaldamist ega &uuml;henduse intellektuaalomandi &otilde;igusi k&auml;sitlevate eeskirjade kohaldamist; </eesti>
